{
  "stem": "5837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, where I was-- I suppose, I think where I-- the school that I went to was-- yeah, it was a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't have any problems there, definitely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very sheltered and protected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't experience anything bad in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, I'm glad you brought this subject of how were Jews treated there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I just feel this is the perfect time for me to bring up this issue, where so many Jews talk about anti-Semitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I am the symbol of-- of the good-- of the good and-- and of the tremendous risk and help that I got from Polish people.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I survived thanks to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lodz, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I did not-- I am nothing but grateful.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] some of the-- my son, my oldest son, Ron, he's really an expert on Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he has read so much about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he says, mom, it is so unfair to what the Jews are saying about the Poles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because when we look at Yad Vashem, at the number of Poles that saved Jewish lives, there's more Poles that saved Jewish lives than any other--",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stayed in Poland until 1950.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then my parents, like many, many Jews at that time, decided to leave Poland and-- and make [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aliyah ?] go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, you know, I remember clearly-- I remember clearly other Jews leaving Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of them were fortunate to come to this country, some went to Canada, and we went to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we arrived in Israel, I believe it was January 1950.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
